{"tid":1374950,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武嘅，係時候進化","createTime":"2019-07-28T02:33:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T02:33:17.000Z","uid":276674,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4565f00faffff391eb81ded8d0b729e7917f2174","tid":1374950,"uid":276674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:33:17.000Z","msg":"每次勇武，最後都係俾人打，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">其實咁係為咩？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n係想打贏警察？<br />\n係想攻入村？<br />\n係想同警察打一輪然後散？<br />\n係想每一次都佔領？<br />\n係想打班警察發洩？<br />\n<br />\n然後和理非又唔明。<br />\n<br />\n七一攻立法會對準政權，和理非明，所以有人守。<br />\n圍警總對準警權，和理非明，所以有人守。<br />\n新城市困獸戰，<br />\n<br />\n但其他行動目的？<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非唔明就唔會幫手。<br />\n</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勇武係時候要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">進化</span></span>，勇武應該建立<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">1. 每次行動目的的論述</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 一套完整的戰術手册</span></span><br />\n<br />\n然後傳俾和理非同前線兄弟。俾和理非明勇武係為咩，咩時候應該勇武，咩時候唔應該武勇。要勇武時前線兄弟點點一齊行動，後面又點行動。"}]}